# American Style Pancakes

## Ingredients
- 1 cup plain flour
- 2 tsp baking powder
- 2 tbsp sugar
- 1/2 tsp salt
- 3/4 cup of milk
- 2 tbsp melted butter or margarine
- 2 eggs (separated)

## Instructions
1. Mix flour, baking powder, sugar and salt in mixing bowl. Set aside
2. Stir together milk, melted butter and egg yolks
3. Whisk egg whites to make all fluffy and happy
4. Stir milk mixture into flour mixture and fold in egg whites. The batter should hold its shape but not be too stiff.
5. Cook in heated pan until pancakes bubble then turn over
